I love hiking. Especially in places with routes I have never explored. At first, it makes you a little nervous because the wrong choices can result in you being lost in the woods. But something urges you to keep pushing forward. Sometimes this takes you to places that aren't so great. Other times it leads you to places that take your breath away. It is worth the risk. Step and pursue the paths that intrigue you in life so you can experience these moments.

A lot of people have asked why I joined this company. Is it a scam? Is it MLM? 😡 Believe me I researched. I am NOT a salesperson. I AM a multi-tasker, busy wife, mother & grandmother!  However, when I found out about the products and fell in love w/them 🍀 and looked at it like anything else you would purchase from someone on TV or being advertised, I jumped on board. Why?  Because I wanted extra money 💰. I wanted to have the freedom to say YES & the freedom to pay & vacation. I back the products & help people feel good & look good & get paid to do it. 👏👍🏻 so, when someone comes to me & is looking for something to help their skin or health or mind, I can say "here you go" and feel good knowing I've helped them. And when someone wants to make extra cash 💰 I can say "jump on board my team and let me help you!" It's not a get rich quick scheme. Believe me LOL 😂. It takes work like anything else. I am promoting products that I love ❤️ and I am able to do it all from my phone 📱 If you are looking for awesome products or a way to earn extra money, I am here to help!! #itworks #thegoodlife #dreamjob job #sayyes #doit
